    <h2 class="ts-resources__heading text-[clamp(22px,3.5vw,38px)] font-medium tracking-[-0.03em] text-[var(--ez-black)] mb-3">Where to go from here</h2>
    <p class="ts-resources__sub text-[15px] text-[var(--ez-grey)] leading-[1.6] max-w-[52ch] mb-10">If the fix above didn't resolve it, the next path is a file, a guide, or a direct conversation.</p>
    <div class="ts-resource-grid">

      <a href="/pages/downloads" class="ts-resource-card group hover:border-[var(--ez-amber-35)] hover:shadow-[0_8px_28px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)]">
